\v 36 Yilo lelo iphupho; sesizakutsho ingcazelo yalo phambi kwenkosi.
\v 37 Wena, nkosi, uyinkosi yamakhosi\x + Ezra 7.12; Hez. 26.7.\x*, ngoba uNkulunkulu wamazulu\x + 2.18.\x*\x + Ezra 1.2; 5.18.\x* ukunikile umbuso\x + Ezra 1.2; 5.18.\x*, amandla\x + 4.30; Esta 9.29.\x*, lokuqina\x + 4.21; Jer. 27.6.\x*, lodumo\x + 4.30; Esta 9.29.\x*.
\v 38 Njalo loba kungaphi lapho abantwana babantu abahlezi khona, izinyamazana zeganga lezinyoni zamazulu uzinikele esandleni sakho\x + 4.21; Jer. 27.6.\x*, wakwenza waba ngumbusi phezu kwazo zonke. Wena uyilelikhanda legolide\x + 2.32; 3.1; 4.22.\x*.
\v 39 Langemva kwakho kuzavela omunye umbuso\x + 5.28,31; 7.5.\x* omncinyane kulowakho\x + 2.32; 3.1; 4.22.\x*, lomunye owesithathu umbuso\x + 7.6.\x* wethusi\x + 2.32; 3.1; 4.22.\x*, ozabusa emhlabeni wonke.
\v 40 Lombuso wesine uzaqina njengensimbi\x + 7.7,23.\x*; ngoba njengoba insimbi\x + 2.8; 2.41,45; 4.18; 5.12,22; 6.3; 6.4,22.\x* ichoboza yehlisele phansi konke\x + 2.40,44,45; 2.35; Mat. 21.44; Luka 20.18; Isa. 8.9.\x*, njalo njengensimbi echoboza konke lokhu, \add ngokunjalo\add* uzachoboza wephule\x + 2.40,44,45; 2.35; Mat. 21.44; Luka 20.18; Isa. 8.9.\x*.
\v 41 Njalo njengoba wabona izinyawo lamazwane\x + 2.33.\x*, kuyingxenye yebumba lombumbi lengxenye yensimbi, umbuso uzadatshulwa phakathi. Kodwa kuzakuba kuwo okwamandla ensimbi\x + 7.7,23.\x*, njengoba wabona\x + 2.8; 2.41,45; 4.18; 5.12,22; 6.3; 6.4,22.\x* insimbi ihlanganiswe lebumba eliludaka\x + 2.43.\x*.
\v 42 Njengoba amazwane enyawo ayelengxenye yensimbi lengxenye yebumba; umbuso uzakuba lamandla nganxanye, wephuke lula nganxanye.
\v 43 Njalo njengoba wabona insimbi ihlanganiswe lebumba eliludaka\x + 2.43.\x*, bazazihlanganisa lenzalo yabantu\x + Gen. 6.2; Neh. 13.23.\x*, kodwa kabayikunamathelana, njengoba insimbi ingahlanganiswa lebumba\x + 2.43.\x*.
\v 44 Langensuku zalamakhosi uNkulunkulu wamazulu\x + 2.18.\x* uzamisa umbuso\x + 4.3,34; 7.14,27; Mika 4.7; Obad. 21; Luka 1.33; Isa. 60.12; Mika 4.8; Mat. 3.2; Joha. 18.36; 1 Kor. 15.24.\x*\x + 6.26.\x*, ongayikuchithwa\x + 6.26.\x* kuze kube phakade; lombuso kawuyikutshiyelwa abanye abantu; uzachoboza\x + Mika 4.13; Hlab. 2.9.\x* uqede\x + 2.40,44,45; 2.35; Mat. 21.44; Luka 20.18; Isa. 8.9.\x* yonke limibuso\x + Mat. 21.24; Luka 20.18.\x*, wona-ke uzakuma kuze kube phakade\x + 4.3,34; 7.14,27; Mika 4.7; Obad. 21; Luka 1.33; Isa. 60.12; Mika 4.8; Mat. 3.2; Joha. 18.36; 1 Kor. 15.24.\x*.
\v 45 Ngenxa yokuthi\x + 2.8; 2.41,45; 4.18; 5.12,22; 6.3; 6.4,22.\x* wabona\x + 2.34,35.\x* ukuthi ilitshe liqetshulwa entabeni\x + Isa. 28.16; Zek. 3.9; 1 Pet. 2.4,7.\x*, kungengezandla, lokuthi lachoboza insimbi, ithusi, ibumba, isiliva, legolide; uNkulunkulu omkhulu\x + 2.28.\x* uyazisile inkosi okuzakwenzeka emva kwalokhu; iphupho liqinisekile, lengcazelo yalo ithembekile.
