\v 46 Lapho inkosi uNebhukadinezari yathi mbo ngobuso bayo\x + 2 Sam. 14.22; Mat. 8.2; Seb. 10.25.\x*, yakhuleka kuDaniyeli\x + 2 Sam. 14.22; Mat. 8.2; Seb. 10.25.\x*\x + 3.5-7; 3.10-12; 3.14,15,18,28; Isa. 44.15.\x*, yathi kuthululelwe kuye umnikelo\x + Seb. 14.13.\x* lezimpepha\x + Ezra 6.10.\x*.
\v 47 Inkosi yamphendula uDaniyeli, yathi: Kuliqiniso ukuthi uNkulunkulu wenu unguNkulunkulu wabonkulunkulu\x + Dute. 10.17.\x*, leNkosi yamakhosi\x + 1 Tim. 6.15; Isam. 17.14; 19.16.\x*, lomambuli wezimfihlakalo\x + 2.28.\x*, ngoba ubelakho ukwembula limfihlakalo.
